metadata.title: Introduction to Sully Plantation
metadata.synopsis: The speaker introduces himself as David Robinson, residing at 744 Drainesville Road in Herndon, Virginia. He shares that he moved into his house in 1965 and began researching its history due to its age, dating back to the late 1700s. His research led him to Eddie Wagstaff, a resident at Sully Plantation, sparking his interest in the plantation's history and preservation efforts.
